title: We're here...with Stassi!
description:
It's the premiere of Give Them Lala...with Randall! Power couple Lala Kent (Vanderpump Rules) and Randall Emmett (The Irishman) take you beyond the tabloids, into their real lives, and bring some amazing guests along with them. Their very first guest: podcast queen and one of the stars of Vanderpump Rules, Stassi Schroeder!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
